args: The Empire is attacking!\nEverybody, run for the woods!
Incinerate all who oppose the Empire!
You will do no such thing!
I can forgive none who would dismantle\nthe peace of innocents and put their\nhomes to the torch!
Now you will know an equal amount\nof pain and suffering by my hand!

Hot damn, that lady is JUICED!
Still, it ain't the best idea in the world
to go chasin' a pack of imperial soldiers
all by yer lonesome.
Especially when that enemy is a master\nof manipulating fire mana!
We have to help her. Come on!
Tsk! You're stronger than you look; clearly\nwe should have brought greater numbers.\nFall back, men! Fall back!
Princess Fjorm, are you all right?
I love yer brass, lady, but yer gonna give\nus ulcers if ya keep runnin' off like that.
Upon consideration, I may have acted\nrashly. I apologize for being out of line.
We are more than aware of your strength,\nPrincess Fjorm.
However, said strength will be better\nserved by acting in concert with your\nallies, as opposed to wielding it alone.
I am truly sorry. When I saw the village\nin danger, I fear the body simply acted\nwithout consulting the mind.
Your concern for others is admirable.\nWe'd just like you to show some\nconcern for yourself as well.
Blimey, thank you all so much!\nI thought we was done for, so I did!
Happy to help. Please let us know\nif there's anything else we can do.

Well, I'm loathe to mention it after all
what you did for us, but the Empire set
our fields to burn, and we ain't got but
crumbs left to eat.
I'll have supplies sent over\nfrom the Halidom at once.
Us poor peasants ain't worthy\nof such charity, Yer Highness!
There is no need for such restraint.\nI have bread enough to share.
You must divide this amongst yourselves\nfor now, but we will be sending\nadditional supplies posthaste.
Make certain to share with the others!
Was that your share of the bread\nCleo provided us?
Yes. They clearly needed it more than I.
That was very kind of you.
Only one with a heart of stone could\nbear to watch children go without.
The Empire's really been pushing their\nassaults lately.
I do what I can to protect everyone,\nbut I can't be everywhere at once.
...My homeland of Nifl fell victim\nto the cruel fires of Mspell.
To see the same manner of strife claim\nvictims here is disheartening.
The Dyrenell Empire has vast portions\nof this land in disarray.
But we are going to change that.
I know that I will return\nto my home someday.
But until that time comes, I would repay\nyou for the kindness you have shown me.
Let me fight at your side, Your Highness!\nLet me help the people of your land\nin their fight against the Empire!
I refuse to stand by while the weak\nand defenseless suffer so!
We would be honored to have you\nin our ranks, Fjorm.
It will take all of us to forge the\npeaceful world I desire.
I look forward to fighting with you.
